This article is about the type of food store. For the 2006 comic Supermarket,
see _S_u_p_e_r_m_a_r_k_e_t_ _(_c_o_m_i_c_s_). For the album, see _S_u_p_e_r_m_a_r_k_e_t_ _(_a_l_b_u_m_).
